				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2301795/scp-3023#post-4822385</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 19 Nov 2020 13:07:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Gaffsey</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6590029</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Articles like this, where it seems like the author just had an idea for &quot;wouldn't it be weird if _?&quot; and then just nailed the execution, are low-key some of my favorite on the site. If I had to have one complaint, I think that A-19 would have been a much stronger ending than the &quot;here's how it happened&#8230; maybe&quot; bit. Still, thoroughly enjoyable, deeply strange, and delightfully inexplicable make for an easy +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
