					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The map isn't just a spider, it's a spider that has the Brocken Mountain as its center of mass, this mountain is the prime location for witches sabbaths in German folklore. It was also a predominant pagan sacrificial site to Wotan/Odin. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brocken">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brocken</a>. Well done!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
